Omega Generator - Tier 1 Schematic 
===================================================
Version: Alpha Release
Purpose: Portable, entry-level piezoelectric energy device based on crystal resonance and magnetic field amplification. Designed for replication and experimentation.

---------------------------------------------------
1. Core Components
---------------------------------------------------
- 1x Langasite or Quartz crystal rod (30mm x 100mm) - aligned with lattice for max piezoelectric response
- 1x Magnetic ring assembly (Searle-inspired, neodymium or ceramic, toroidal layout)
- 1x Copper coil (flat spiral, 40 turns, 18 AWG, wound around crystal housing)
- 1x Shock housing chamber (acrylic or polycarbonate w/ silicone damping feet)
- 1x External pressure oscillator (manual, weighted, or tuning fork impulse)

---------------------------------------------------
2. Operational Resonance Target
---------------------------------------------------
- Resonant Frequency: 432 Hz (adjustable via tension & coil tuning)
- Harmonic Feedback Loop: yes (feedback through coil reinduction to pressure pad)
- Magnetic Frequency Modulation: via rotational orientation of toroidal ring

---------------------------------------------------
3. Circuit Summary
---------------------------------------------------
1. Crystal encased in vibration chamber
2. Oscillating impact initiates piezoelectric voltage pulse
3. Toroidal magnetic field directs and amplifies pulse
4. Copper coil collects and stores induced charge
5. Output directed to capacitor bank or micro inverter

---------------------------------------------------
4. Build Notes
---------------------------------------------------
- Crystal alignment matters: axis must match natural polarization direction
- Use non-conductive shock dampers to isolate vibration channel
- Maintain toroidal symmetry to avoid magnetic drift
- Optional: use an oscilloscope to tune crystal impact to harmonic peak
- Safe output target: 2-10V at 10-100mA under ideal mechanical stress

---------------------------------------------------
5. Modular Expansion Points
---------------------------------------------------
- Add resonance feedback tuner (acoustic microphone or LVDT)
- Integrate energy storage via supercapacitor
- Magnetic levitation base for frictionless tuning
- Vacuum enclosure to eliminate field disruption

---------------------------------------------------
6. Licensing & Intent
---------------------------------------------------
